Nio has consistently refuted rumors of any alliance with Mercedes-Benz on numerous occasions in the past.Speculation surrounding a potential Nio-Mercedes collaboration has been circulating for several months  primarily fueled by an image capturing a meeting between Mercedes CEO Ola Kllenius and Nio CEO William Li at a Nio House.
